commit.message:
composite-type.c: Pass -Wno-unused.

gcc/testsuite/
	* gcc.dg/fixed-point/composite-type.c: Pass -Wno-unused.
	* gcc.dg/fixed-point/struct-union.c: Update error messages.

From-SVN: r168876
